---
// 关于我们组件 - 2025现代设计
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    
    <!-- 标题区域 -->
    <div class="section-header text-center mb-48">
      <div class="section-badge animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <span class="badge-icon">💡</span>
        <span class="badge-text">关于我们</span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="section-title animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
        创新赋能效率
        <span class="gradient-text">持续追求卓越</span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="section-subtitle animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
        通过前沿技术重塑跨境物流网络，打造透明、可靠、高效的全球物流体系
      </p>
      
      <p class="section-description animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
        Innovation Drives Efficiency, Continuous Pursuit of Excellence
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 关于我们内容 -->
    <div class="about-content animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
      <div class="content-grid">
        
        <!-- 左侧文字内容 -->
        <div class="content-text">
          <div class="about-description">
            <p class="description-text">
              HPF KZ 致力于通过前沿技术重塑跨境物流网络。我们相信，真正的效率源于对细节的极致追求和对技术的持续创新。
            </p>
            
            <p class="description-text">
              在这个数据驱动的时代，我们利用人工智能、区块链和物联网技术，打造透明、可靠、高效的全球物流体系。我们不满足于现状，始终追求卓越。
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="stats-grid">
              <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">5+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">年深耕</div>
                <div class="stat-sublabel">Years of Excellence</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">项目成功</div>
                <div class="stat-sublabel">Successful Projects</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">99%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">客户满意度</div>
                <div class="stat-sublabel">Client Satisfaction</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="about-cta">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
              <span class="btn-text">开启合作</span>
              <span class="btn-icon">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 右侧视觉元素 -->
        <div class="content-visual">
          <div class="visual-container">
            
            <!-- 主要视觉元素 -->
            <div class="main-visual">
              <div class="network-diagram">
                <!-- 中心节点 -->
                <div class="center-node">
                  <div class="node-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                      <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="node-label">HPF</div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- 连接节点 -->
                <div class="connection-node node-1">
                  <div class="node-dot"></div>
                  <div class="node-label">物流</div>
                </div>
                <div class="connection-node node-2">
                  <div class="node-dot"></div>
                  <div class="node-label">技术</div>
                </div>
                <div class="connection-node node-3">
                  <div class="node-dot"></div>
                  <div class="node-label">创新</div>
                </div>
                <div class="connection-node node-4">
                  <div class="node-dot"></div>
                  <div class="node-label">效率</div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- 连接线 -->
                <div class="connection-line line-1"></div>
                <div class="connection-line line-2"></div>
                <div class="connection-line line-3"></div>
                <div class="connection-line line-4"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 装饰性元素 -->
            <div class="visual-decorations">
              <div class="decoration dec-1"></div>
              <div class="decoration dec-2"></div>
              <div class="decoration dec-3"></div>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 企业文化 -->
    <div class="culture-section animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 1.2s;">
      <div class="culture-header text-center">
        <h3 class="culture-title">企业价值观</h3>
        <p class="culture-subtitle">Corporate Values</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="culture-grid">
        <div class="culture-item">
          <div class="culture-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="culture-name">创新突破</h4>
          <p class="culture-description">勇于挑战现状，持续创新技术与服务</p>
          <p class="culture-subtitle">Innovation & Breakthrough</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="culture-item">
          <div class="culture-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="culture-name">卓越服务</h4>
          <p class="culture-description">以客户为中心，提供极致体验与价值</p>
          <p class="culture-subtitle">Excellence in Service</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="culture-item">
          <div class="culture-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="10"></line>
              <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="4"></line>
              <line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="16"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="culture-name">高效执行</h4>
          <p class="culture-description">快速响应市场变化，精准高效执行策略</p>
          <p class="culture-subtitle">Efficient Execution</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: var(--space-48) 0;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }
  
  /* 标题区域 */
  .section-badge {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .section-badge .badge-content {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    background: var(--bg-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, var(--text-6xl));
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, var(--text-2xl));
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .section-description {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  /* 内容区域 */
  .about-content {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
  }
  
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-24);
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  /* 文字内容 */
  .content-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-16);
  }
  
  .about-description {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .description-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  
  /* 统计数据 */
  .about-stats {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .stat-number {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .stat-label {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }
  
  .stat-sublabel {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  
  /* CTA按钮 */
  .about-cta {
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  
  .about-cta .btn {
    min-width: 160px;
  }
  
  /* 视觉元素 */
  .content-visual {
    position: relative;
    height: 500px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .visual-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .main-visual {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
  }
  
  .network-diagram {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  /* 中心节点 */
  .center-node {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .node-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  
  .node-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  /* 连接节点 */
  .connection-node {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-1);
  }
  
  .node-dot {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .node-1 {
    top: 20%;
    left: 20%;
  }
  
  .node-2 {
    top: 20%;
    right: 20%;
  }
  
  .node-3 {
    bottom: 20%;
    left: 20%;
  }
  
  .node-4 {
    bottom: 20%;
    right: 20%;
  }
  
  /* 连接线 */
  .connection-line {
    position: absolute;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-accent), transparent);
    height: 2px;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }
  
  .line-1 {
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 80px;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-45deg);
  }
  
  .line-2 {
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 80px;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(45deg);
  }
  
  .line-3 {
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 80px;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-135deg);
  }
  
  .line-4 {
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 80px;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(135deg);
  }
  
  /* 装饰元素 */
  .visual-decorations {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .decoration {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-accent);
    opacity: 0.3;
  }
  
  .dec-1 {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    top: 10%;
    left: 10%;
  }
  
  .dec-2 {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    bottom: 15%;
    right: 10%;
  }
  
  .dec-3 {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    top: 50%;
    left: 80%;
  }
  
  /* 企业文化 */
  .culture-section {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-3xl);
    padding: var(--space-24);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .culture-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }
  
  .culture-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .culture-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  
  .culture-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .culture-item {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s var(--ease-out);
  }
  
  .culture-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  
  .culture-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .culture-name {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .culture-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  /* 响应式设计 */
  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-16);
    }
    
    .content-visual {
      order: -1;
      height: 400px;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section {
      padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    }
    
    .about-content {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-24);
    }
    
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
    
    .culture-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }
    
    .culture-section {
      padding: var(--space-16);
    }
    
    .content-visual {
      height: 300px;
    }
    
    .network-diagram {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .content-visual {
      height: 250px;
    }
    
    .network-diagram {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
    
    .culture-section {
      padding: var(--space-8);
    }
  }
</style>